0000</guid></item><item><title>西班牙和以色列考古学家揭开了Qesem洞穴骨骺缺失之谜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-30/ty-article/spanish-and-israeli-archaeologists-crack-mystery-of-missing-epiphyses-in-qesem-cave/0000018f-2ed2-dc45-a78f-3edb77780000</link><description>在以色列中部的一个洞穴中，考古学家发现了一个异常现象。古人类住在洞穴里并吃动物。美好的。但是动物腿骨的末端发生了什么？这就是油脂的史前史。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:41:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-30/ty-article/spanish-and-israeli-archaeologists-crack-mystery-of-missing-epiphyses-in-qesem-cave/0000018f-2ed2-dc45-a78f-3edb77780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察在耶路撒冷老城被土耳其公民刺伤；约旦河西岸发生汽车冲撞事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-stabbed-in-jerusalem-by-turkish-citizen-car-ramming-attempt-in-west-bank/0000018f-2ead-dc45-a78f-3eed7b720000</link><description>警方消息人士称，被警方击毙的袭击者是一名土耳其公民，在过去 72 小时内抵达以色列，很可能是一名游客</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/police-officer-stabbed-in-jerusalem-by-turkish-citizen-car-ramming-attempt-in-west-bank/0000018f-2ead-dc45-a78f-3eed7b720000</guid></item><item><title>埃及的提议让内塔尼亚胡陷入困境，但真正必须做出决定的是甘茨和艾森科特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/egypts-proposal-puts-netanyahu-in-a-bind-but-its-eisenkot-and-gantz-who-really-decide/0000018f-2e17-df35-a1af-3ef77ffb0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道，与哈马斯达成停火协议可能对其政府宣判死刑，因此甘茨和艾森科特现在是兑现承诺，将人质带回家并促成达成协议的时候了</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 10:10:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/egypts-proposal-puts-netanyahu-in-a-bind-but-its-eisenkot-and-gantz-who-really-decide/0000018f-2e17-df35-a1af-3ef77ffb0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在拜登和以色列极右翼之间左右为难，不情愿地权衡他曾经驳回的人质协议提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/torn-between-biden-and-the-israeli-right-netanyahu-weighs-proposals-he-once-ruled-out/0000018f-2b6e-d8c4-afef-2ffecfab0000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯的团队在过去一周都表现出了更大的灵活性，但内塔尼亚胡仍然受到他的极右伙伴的克制，他们要求在拉法采取行动——尽管以色列国防军有所保留——甚至不惜以人质交易为代价甚至可能是沙特的正常化</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/torn-between-biden-and-the-israeli-right-netanyahu-weighs-proposals-he-once-ruled-out/0000018f-2b6e-d8c4-afef-2ffecfab0000</guid></item><item><title>国务卿布林肯抵达以色列，哈马斯提出停火要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article-live/u-s-does-not-believe-icc-has-jurisdiction-to-issue-warrants-against-israeli-officials/0000018f-2cb3-dc45-a78f-3efb99c00000</link><description>以色列警察在耶路撒冷刺伤事件中受中伤；袭击者疑为土耳其国民 ■ 以色列官员：在哈马斯做出反应之前，加沙谈判代表团不会前往开罗 ■ 抗议者冲进哥伦比亚大学汉密尔顿大厅，反战示威升级 ■ 拜登对卡塔尔和埃及领导人：人质协议是“唯一障碍”以色列与哈马斯停火</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-30/ty-article-live/u-s-does-not-believe-icc-has-jurisdiction-to-issue-warrants-against-israeli-officials/0000018f-2cb3-dc45-a78f-3efb99c00000</guid></item><item><title>学生们不顾因“加沙营地”而停学的威胁，将自己设置在哥伦比亚大学校园内</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/despite-suspensions-student-protesters-refuse-to-leave-gaza-encampment-at-columbia/0000018f-2ca1-d502-a5bf-ece7ffd60001</link><description>随着拆除抗议营地的最后期限过去，数十名学生仍留在原地过夜。针对哥伦比亚大学受托人提起集体诉讼，指控其未拆除营地，从而剥夺了犹太学生安全的学习环境</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:40:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/despite-suspensions-student-protesters-refuse-to-leave-gaza-encampment-at-columbia/0000018f-2ca1-d502-a5bf-ece7ffd60001</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学表示已开始停课“加沙团结营地”的学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-30/ty-article/.premium/columbia-says-it-has-begun-suspending-students-at-gaza-solidarity-encampment/0000018f-2b8f-dc45-a78f-3fc